for each node, \f(CW\*(C`sub\*(C'\fR is changed to \f(CW\*(C`val\*(C'\fR.  \f(CW\*(C`sub\*(C'\fR may also be \f(CW\*(C`NULL\*(C'\fR
in which case the \f(CW\*(C`base\*(C'\fR nodes are modified.
