.Sp
For more information on states, see \fIguestfs\fR\|(3).
.ie n .IP "$flag = $g\->is_socket ($path [, followsymlinks => $followsymlinks]);" 4
.el .IP "\f(CW$flag\fR = \f(CW$g\fR\->is_socket ($path [, followsymlinks => \f(CW$followsymlinks\fR]);" 4
