.IX Item "$g->mkfifo ($mode, $path);"
This call creates a \s-1FIFO\s0 (named pipe) called \f(CW\*(C`path\*(C'\fR with
mode \f(CW\*(C`mode\*(C'\fR.  It is just a convenient wrapper around
\&\f(CW\*(C`$g\->mknod\*(C'\fR.
.Sp
